original_title: Pirate Hunters: The U.S. Navy SEALs Rescue of Captain Phillips & the Maersk Alabama
overview: The harrowing rescue of Captain Phillips and crew after their U.S. cargo ship was overtaken by pirates is recounted by the Navy SEALs who took part.
title: Pirate Hunters: The U.S. Navy SEALs Rescue of Captain Phillips & the Maersk Alabama
